title: backyard garden planning + seed starting day
summary: this content is my friend and i getting my backyard set up, specifically getting measurements to create a layout of what the garden & backyard could look like. she also helped me plant my seeds indoors, so that i can transplant them when they germinate. hopefully it turns out well, but i also give tips on how to start your seeds. im starting to grow green onions,leeks, red lettuce, and arugula
